Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  不对  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下中了查拉奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\pos(743,643)\fn微软雅黑}即死咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澄夜  不是那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,180度查欧拉鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\pos(690,643)\fn微软雅黑}弱复活咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  应该是180度查欧立克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\pos(782,643)\fn微软雅黑}大复活咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  哪个都无所谓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动啊  就站在那里别动  公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在这儿别动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝基拉玛
